  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To prepare students for their future, it is crucial that (computing) education not only enables them to understand the digital world surrounding them but to actively shape this world.",
    "Given the immense impact of AI/ML systems on our daily lives, this includes empowering students to creatively design and develop such systems themselves.",
    "To this end, relevant AI/ML-related competencies are being discussed and introduced in K-12 computer science curricula around the world (e.g., Touretzky et al., 2019; Tedre et al., 2021; Michaeli et al., 2023).",
    "Also, a plethora of educational resources and approaches has been developed in recent years (Morales-Navarro et al., 2024).",
    "However, we still lack an understanding of problems teachers and students face in the classroom, in particular when designing AI/ML systems."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "To this end, relevant AI/ML-related competencies are being discussed and introduced in K-12 computer science curricula around the world (e.g., Touretzky et al., 2019; Tedre et al., 2021; Michaeli et al., 2023).",
